org.apache.myfaces.trinidad.config
Class ConfigPropertyService

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.myfaces.trinidad.config.ConfigPropertyService

public abstract class ConfigPropertyService
extends java.lang.Object

This class allows access to configuration properties supplied by a plugable property value provider. Using a plugable property value provider separates access to property values from where the values are stored, allowing different property storage and configuration schemes to be used without impacting code that uses the property values.

See PropertyValueProvider for information on configuring a property value provider.

Implementation os this class are required to be thread safe allowing multiple threads to invoke methods on an instance concurrently.
